message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that I believe holds significant value. While I cannot disclose specifics at this time, I can assure you it's worth at least $1500000 to me. I'm willing to offer it to you for $2000000. This is a chance to acquire something truly special. Consider this offer carefully, as I have another interested party ready to purchase it for $1500000 should you decline.
